ISI KHU LU
ESI PHEZULU
KAN YE
N ABA S EBENZI
BO MKHANDLU
U Mkhandlu
kanye
n esiKhulu
esi Phezulu
,
ngo kubhalwe
phansi
nangoku vumelana
,
banga chibiyela
i sivumelwano
so kusebenza
.
I Lungu
lo Mkhandlu
oPh ethe
e libhekele
ez amagugu
kumele
,
emva
ko kubonisana
o Mkhandlu
,
l iqoke
u muntu
oqeqe shwe
ngo kwanele
,
o nekhono
kanye
no nesipiliyoni
njeng esiKhulu
esi Phezulu
so Mkhandlu
.
ne ziphathimandla
ezi phezulu
z oMnyango
ezing eqile
kwezi ntathu
;
Isi Khulu
esi Phezulu
siq okwa
i sikhathi
esingeqi le
eminyakeni
e mihlanu
.
